Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.55,0:00:10.99,italics,nar,0000,0000,0000,,It appeared as though humanity \Nwould be destroyed by the demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.95,0:00:19.20,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,But a single mage saved them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.34,0:00:31.51,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,He was called the Wizard King,\Nand he became a legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.92,0:00:39.39,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,The forces of the Eye of the Midnight \NSun attacked the Witches' Forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.39,0:00:42.93,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,They were after the magic stone \Nthat lies in the forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.67,0:00:49.04,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,At the same time, the forces of the Diamond \NKingdom also attacked the Witches' Forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.04,0:00:51.53,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,They wanted to take advantage of the chaos
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.53,0:00:54.61,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,and steal the Queen of Witches' secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.14,0:00:58.12,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Fanzell, a former officer in \Nthe Diamond Kingdom's army,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.12,0:01:02.12,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,ended up facing two of his \Nformer students, Mars and Ladros.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.12,0:01:04.00,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,Million Lasers!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.17,0:01:14.21,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Don't... You should be using your \Npowers to do the right thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.21,0:01:20.25,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,Getting to use your power to the max in \Ncombat... What could be better than that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.25,0:01:24.43,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,You see, I want to be acknowledged. \NBy this country! By this world!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.39,0:01:29.69,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,Guess I'll just have to kill this chick first!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.77,0:01:33.32,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.90,0:01:39.78,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,My powers... exist to protect others.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.33,0:01:43.54,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,Your lessons got through to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.81,0:01:47.47,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Mars managed to turn the \Ntables at the last moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.47,0:01:49.13,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Fanzell was troubled because
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.13,0:01:53.73,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,he thought there was no way to defeat \NLadros's absorption and emission power,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.73,0:01:55.42,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,but he and Mars came up with a plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.42,0:01:57.93,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,What are you gossiping about over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.93,0:02:02.85,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what plan you come up with,\Nit'll be useless against my power!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.85,0:02:06.32,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not half bad at \Nreinforcement magic myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.32,0:02:07.52,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Have a nice trip!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.32,0:02:23.74,Ep Title,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1023,1)}The Promised World
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.95,0:03:46.34,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,We have you completely surrounded!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.34,0:03:49.20,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,So just give up already!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.20,0:03:53.29,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,If you do something stupid, your parents \Nand friends back home will be sad!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.29,0:03:58.84,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,You filthy humans... Don't you\N dare speak of my friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.27,0:04:07.76,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,She still has that much magic left?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.76,0:04:09.68,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.97,0:04:16.05,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,Those flames...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.05,0:04:17.40,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,There! They're right over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.73,0:04:20.90,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,This overwhelming amount of magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.80,0:04:22.90,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,It's Salamander!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.26,0:04:25.70,main,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,This magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.34,0:04:29.91,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,In that situation, Asta's not going \Nto have any time to deal with Ladros!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.41,0:04:33.46,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,No, wait a sec...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.42,0:04:38.42,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Teach! Mars! Wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.42,0:04:41.83,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,A little reinforcement magic \Nwon't help you win against me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.83,0:04:44.05,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,And you'll never win if \Nyou keep running away!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.05,0:04:47.89,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go! Million Lasers!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.85,0:04:56.31,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.31,0:04:57.81,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Old Man Zell!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.37,0:05:00.98,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, you're with the pale guy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.19,0:05:05.07,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.16,0:05:10.87,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Deflect it over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.87,0:05:13.04,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what's going on, but okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.67,0:05:18.42,italics,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get us out of the way using the wind
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.77,0:05:20.92,italics,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,and aim the fire right at...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.17,0:05:25.13,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... This is way too big!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.56,0:05:36.78,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Did it work?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.21,0:05:45.14,italics,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Ladros's magical powers disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.94,0:05:48.97,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Old Man Zell!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.97,0:05:52.73,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck's going on here?!\NSomething just fell!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.73,0:05:54.61,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Well done, Asta.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.61,0:05:56.34,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,I see you've grown even stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.34,0:05:58.33,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, shucks. It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.05,0:06:03.28,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,No, wait! Why are you with the pale guy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.28,0:06:04.42,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,He's an enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.37,0:06:10.55,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,Asta, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.09,0:06:14.10,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,I am not your enemy. Trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.10,0:06:17.06,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,How am I supposed to believe a \Nguy with an evil face like yours?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.45,0:06:20.20,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,And my name is Mars, you shrimp.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.20,0:06:22.06,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, your mouth's nasty now, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.40,0:06:24.02,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,I'll explain everything later.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.02,0:06:24.82,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.49,0:06:28.07,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,For now, I'd like you to trust Mars.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.54,0:06:31.83,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if you say so.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.58,0:06:35.67,main,Zell,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks. Now, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.67,0:06:39.09,main,Zell,0000,0000,0000,,I think Ladros has been taken \Ncare of for now, thanks to Asta.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.72,0:06:44.13,main,Zell,0000,0000,0000,,So we need to do something \Nabout this monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.73,0:06:48.80,italics,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,So that's the fire spirit Salamander \Nthat I've heard so much about.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.30,0:06:53.55,italics,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,It appears to be weakened, but it \Nstill has tremendous magical powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.93,0:06:58.06,italics,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,But those flames... They're the same as mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.53,0:07:01.19,italics,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,And this magic itself feels like...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.12,0:07:07.77,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,Fa...na...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.07,0:07:33.80,flashbackitalics,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,We have no family... \Nso we have no other choice...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.80,0:07:34.93,flashbackitalics,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.43,0:07:39.22,flashback,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,Mars, is the training painful?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.39,0:07:42.28,flashback,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, it's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.28,0:07:45.94,flashback,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,When things get rough,\Nremember the faces of those you love.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.47,0:07:51.46,flashback,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,We were born to protect the people \Nof this kingdom that we love so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.66,0:07:54.03,italics,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,The faces of those you love...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.71,0:07:58.71,italics,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,The face that popped into my \Nhead immediately... was yours,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.71,0:07:59.54,italics,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,Fana.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.41,0:08:02.79,flashback,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,Once we become strong enough\N to protect this kingdom,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.79,0:08:05.38,flashback,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,we'll be allowed to go outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.77,0:08:08.71,flashback,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,You'll probably make it out first, Mars.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.71,0:08:09.59,flashback,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,Lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.49,0:08:15.19,flashback,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, you're the strongest \Nout of all of us, Mars.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.75,0:08:20.60,flashback,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be waiting for you when that happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.60,0:08:21.72,flashback,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.72,0:08:24.45,flashback,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,Until you get out, too, Fana.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.58,0:08:29.73,flashback,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,Sure! Let's go see the \Noutside world together.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.68,0:08:38.66,flashback,Trainer,0000,0000,0000,,This is your final test.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.66,0:08:40.12,flashback,Trainer,0000,0000,0000,,Kill each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.92,0:08:46.08,flashback,Trainer,0000,0000,0000,,The sole survivor will be allowed to go \Noutside as our kingdom's mage warrior.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.74,0:08:49.11,flashback,Trainer,0000,0000,0000,,If you refuse, you'll all be disposed of.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.37,0:09:03.69,flashback,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Mars.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.64,0:09:06.96,flashback,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,Fana...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.96,0:09:08.44,flashback,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,I have no other choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.21,0:09:10.31,flashback,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,Please die.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.29,0:09:48.28,flashback,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.09,0:09:50.01,flashback,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.47,0:09:57.41,flashback,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,My wounds...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.94,0:10:01.66,flashback,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,If I didn't do that, you wouldn't have...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.66,0:10:04.16,flashback,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,tried to kill me...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.38,0:10:08.45,flashback,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure you go see the world outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.61,0:10:12.73,flashback,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,For me... as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.47,0:10:20.90,flashback,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,Fana!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.59,0:10:26.81,italics,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I killed her with my own hands...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.14,0:10:30.31,italics,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,But Fana's alive?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.31,0:10:33.44,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,Fana!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.82,0:10:35.96,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.96,0:10:37.61,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,It's me! It's me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.61,0:10:38.53,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you recognize me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.53,0:10:41.24,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,H-H-Hey! Wait, wait, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.24,0:10:42.58,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to die, die, die!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.58,0:10:44.12,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Were you always like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.12,0:10:45.02,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,Fana!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.02,0:10:45.95,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You know each other?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.29,0:10:50.58,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,Fana! Fana!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.38,0:10:50.58,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,He—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.44,0:10:53.75,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,Fana!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.25,0:10:55.25,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Fana?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.88,0:10:58.05,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,My student Fana?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.61,0:11:05.39,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,After I left, I heard she died in \NMorris's human experiments.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.39,0:11:07.89,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,Fana!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.33,0:11:10.77,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.87,0:11:16.61,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Hot, hot, hot, hot, hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.05,0:11:19.55,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,It really is Fana...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.55,0:11:22.39,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,But is that transformation magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.39,0:11:26.12,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,No... there'd be no point in that.\N Or there shouldn't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.63,0:11:29.92,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,That eye is emitting a strange power...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.92,0:11:31.62,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Is it someone's spell?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.38,0:11:38.15,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Is the Eye of the Midnight Sun \Ncontrolling Fana with that eye?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.76,0:11:41.83,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,What... is this? My head is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.48,0:11:44.64,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,Fana!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.14,0:11:51.06,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,Why do all of you insist \Non getting in my way?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.97,0:11:53.15,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,I hate you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.80,0:11:58.86,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.86,0:12:01.57,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Gah! More self-destruct magic?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.13,0:12:06.15,flashback,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,I'm taking you all down with me... No...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.15,0:12:09.20,flashback,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,I'll blow this whole temple to smithereens!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.56,0:12:10.62,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Self-destruct?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.50,0:12:13.53,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with those people?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.53,0:12:16.07,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Do they all come with that option installed?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.07,0:12:19.88,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't good! In a few minutes,\Nthis whole area's going to be blown away!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.44,0:12:22.88,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,Everything should just... disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.37,0:12:33.89,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,Everything should just... disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.98,0:12:42.44,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Sea Dragon's Lair!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.50,0:12:47.87,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Mars, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.85,0:12:55.17,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.00,0:12:59.04,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Block it with your magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.49,0:13:02.81,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,Master, I have no right to block it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.25,0:13:07.43,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,I killed Fana! I can't—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.57,0:13:11.73,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,This is seriously not the time for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.73,0:13:13.64,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Are you stupid?! Do you wanna die?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.31,0:13:18.86,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know the details, \Nbut do you really know her?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.73,0:13:22.52,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,She's a leader in a terrorist group \Ncalled the Eye of the Midnight Sun!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.52,0:13:24.09,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure she's not just similar-looking?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.09,0:13:25.40,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Dude, she's got three eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.76,0:13:28.07,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,I would never mistake Fana!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.07,0:13:30.66,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,She's my precious childhood friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.50,0:13:36.33,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.33,0:13:37.17,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.71,0:13:42.89,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,If she's so important to you,\Nnow's really no time for you to be dying!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.89,0:13:46.07,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Live and save her for real!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.13,0:13:50.18,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,You're right. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.16,0:13:52.93,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Were you always this up-front?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.28,0:13:58.44,italics,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Not only does Asta yell at me,\Nbut now he's yelling at you, his senior.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.97,0:14:01.19,italics,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right, Mars.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.19,0:14:03.94,italics,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be able to save her!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.94,0:14:09.53,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Neither Finral's spatial magic nor my \Nthread magic work against those flames.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.02,0:14:14.04,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,And if we agitate it with Noelle's water \Nmagic, it might explode immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.04,0:14:18.29,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it. Only Asta's \Nanti-magic sword can stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.29,0:14:22.04,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,All right, let's do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.04,0:14:23.80,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.15,0:14:26.09,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,When we fought the hairy gorilla...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.12,0:14:27.54,flashback,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.54,0:14:32.80,flashback,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,You humans shall taste despair... Despair!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.57,0:14:36.10,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,My power couldn't stop him, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.10,0:14:39.23,italics,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,Back then, I ended up killing her, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.40,0:14:50.49,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,This time...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.49,0:14:51.49,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,...I'm not...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.49,0:14:53.49,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,...letting anyone die!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.28,0:14:58.54,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,Stay away from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.71,0:15:04.53,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,Mineral Creation Magic: Laevateinn!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.38,0:15:13.56,italics,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,They're both amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.56,0:15:16.89,italics,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,High-powered flame magic even \Nat that range isn't fazing them!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.23,0:15:20.13,italics,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Still, they have only a few minutes left.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.13,0:15:21.39,italics,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Will they make it in time?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.60,0:15:28.99,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'll charge in until she's in my sword's \Nrange and dispel that self-destruct spell!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.84,0:15:34.39,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,This heat is insane!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.39,0:15:37.04,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,If we go any further, \Nwe'll end up as charcoal!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.66,0:15:39.91,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Asta?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.91,0:15:41.79,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.24,0:15:46.04,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.19,0:15:50.84,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,Flame Recovery Magic: Phoenix Robe.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.29,0:15:54.09,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,You good to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.09,0:15:55.15,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Heck, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.15,0:15:58.58,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,So long as I don't turn into charcoal, \NI can go as far as you want me to!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.25,0:16:06.61,italics,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,This guy's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.05,0:16:12.36,italics,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,After I fought him in the dungeon, I battled \Nagainst many other skilled fighters,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.03,0:16:15.05,top,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet! I'm not done yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.64,0:16:16.66,italics,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,but I've never met anyone \Nwho's this bad at giving up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.66,0:16:18.87,italics,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,And... he's also strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.67,0:16:24.02,italics,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,Even now, he's still not sure whether I'm friend or foe, but he's still talking to me
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.02,0:16:25.49,italics,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,and trying to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.39,0:16:29.38,italics,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,I've fought many of the Magic Knights,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.23,0:16:34.38,italics,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,but no one has tried as hard to \Nprotect and help people as he does.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.16,0:16:38.39,italics,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,He embodies the title in the \Ntruest sense of the term.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.98,0:16:40.29,italics,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,He is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.16,0:16:43.14,italics,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,a real knight!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.43,0:16:47.15,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.15,0:16:49.23,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.23,0:16:53.90,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,This pain can't even begin \Nto compare to Fana's!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.90,0:16:58.23,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,This guy's completely different \Nfrom when I first fought him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.23,0:17:02.91,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,He was like a killer doll back then.\NI didn't know he had such warm feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.62,0:17:05.74,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Enormous, polished power,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.74,0:17:08.42,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,and an unbreakable determination \Nto save someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.74,0:17:11.92,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, he's indestructible!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.17,0:17:16.51,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,It's going to blow any second now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.51,0:17:18.69,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,You guys should evacuate!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.63,0:17:30.79,italics,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,They believe in their friend \Nand refuse to move.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.68,0:17:36.45,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,I'll believe in those two as well,\N and see this through.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.92,0:17:39.90,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Go forth, my students.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.90,0:17:42.45,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,You can do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.46,0:17:49.11,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Just...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.11,0:17:50.46,italics,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,...a little more.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.92,0:17:58.84,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,Fana!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.84,0:18:02.10,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,It's all over.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.10,0:18:05.77,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,No... Not yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.96,0:18:14.03,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let it end!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.49,0:18:26.58,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,H-He did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.58,0:18:28.08,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Ack! Hot, hot, hot! Hot, hot, hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.89,0:18:35.46,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,It's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.83,0:18:36.97,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,It is not gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.48,0:18:42.80,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,Our hatred will never go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.62,0:18:44.60,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Not—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.86,0:18:56.11,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,Fana, it's me! It's me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.11,0:18:58.17,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really, truly sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.17,0:19:01.36,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,Back then, I didn't have the \Nstrength to fight alongside you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.05,0:19:04.13,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,Please forgive me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.20,0:19:09.87,flashback,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,You're a girl, Fana. You shouldn't \Npush yourself too hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.44,0:19:12.35,flashback,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be waiting for you when that happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.35,0:19:14.13,flashback,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,Until you get out, too, Fana.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.09,0:19:23.25,flashback,Elf 2,0000,0000,0000,,Why... Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.25,0:19:26.06,flashback,Elf 4,0000,0000,0000,,Only that human knows where we live!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.06,0:19:28.60,flashback,Elf 5,0000,0000,0000,,He... He must've betrayed us!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.81,0:19:36.51,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,We've met in the outside world,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.51,0:19:38.36,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,but nothing's started yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.36,0:19:39.36,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,Let's...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.82,0:19:41.82,flashback,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go see the \Noutside world together.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.82,0:19:44.02,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go see the world together!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.08,0:20:16.88,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.92,0:20:21.36,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,It's a promise, Mars.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.64,0:20:27.85,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, Fana.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.14,0:20:30.58,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,Mars?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.80,0:20:45.83,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.83,0:20:47.59,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,What a relief.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.59,0:20:48.89,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so jealous!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.91,0:22:36.41,sign_33083_276_Petit_Clover_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,520)}Pe{\c&H3BC020&}t{\c&HE2AF0F&}i{\c&H3BC020&}t C{\c&HE2AF0F&}l{\c&H3BC020&}o{\c&H0E42D4&}ve{\c&H3BC020&}r
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.34,0:22:35.21,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Petit Clover!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.91,0:22:39.92,sign_33188_278_The_Mystery_of_t,Sgn,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(520,1)}Leave It to Mars
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.03,0:22:38.68,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,Leave It to Mars.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.55,0:22:44.17,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Mars. Tell me what happened after \Nyou defeated me all those years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.42,0:22:45.96,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.69,0:22:50.28,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry I defeated you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.28,0:22:51.43,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,Ahem...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.43,0:22:53.76,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,Ta-da! Look at this grimoire!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.15,0:22:56.77,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, is half of this mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.77,0:23:00.49,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! It's a grimoire with your powers in it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.49,0:23:02.31,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,I can feel you all the time!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.62,0:23:04.57,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,Wow... That's a little scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.82,0:23:06.00,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.00,0:23:09.32,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,Th-The mage scholar Morris made this!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.36,0:23:14.44,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,I was brainwashed by Morris.\NThey modified my body,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.44,0:23:16.68,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,and I fought as I was commanded.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.51,0:23:20.83,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,But then I regained my memories \Nafter fighting Asta.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.83,0:23:22.41,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,And ever since, Fana,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.41,0:23:27.22,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,I've been saving lives in secret between \Nmissions as my way of atoning to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.22,0:23:28.17,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a good boy, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.49,0:23:30.47,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, you're a very good boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.18,0:23:33.89,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,You may have defeated me,\N but you're a good boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.24,0:23:35.49,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.38,0:23:41.73,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so jealous... No, envious!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.73,0:23:44.41,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,No, no. I'm older here, so I \Nhave to act like I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.41,0:23:46.71,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,I {\i1}am{\i0} older than Mars, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.71,0:23:49.31,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations, Mars and Fana.\NI wish you happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.31,0:23:52.07,main,Witch queen,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Black Clover{\i0}, Page 62: \N"Those Who Boost Each Other Up."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.07,0:23:54.25,sign_34238_338_Page_2_The_Boys_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(234,1)}Page 62\N\N{\fs18} Those Who Boost Each Other Up
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.07,0:23:53.82,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,No, wait! I {\i1}am{\i0} jealous!
